To analyze a suspicious API request, you can use Swagger to simulate the request and analyze the response. Here's an example:
```javascript
# Load the API request in Swagger
var request = {
  method: "GET",
  url: "https://api.example.com/data",
  headers: {
    "Authorization": "Bearer <token>"
  }
};
Swagger.request(request, function(response) {
  console.log(response);
});
```
